scripts.name: mobile browser touch gestures (English translated)
scripts.description: Add touch gesture functions to mobile browsers, such as ↓↑back to top, ↑↓back to bottom, →←back, ←→forward, →↓close tab, →↑restore the page just closed, etc. There are text gestures, image gestures, video gestures and more. You can also customize your gestures. Kiwi browser, Yandex browser and Lemur browser are recommended.
